Parting words to close up this thread, @KaijuKingz.. Good luck for the mint and may the contract never fail (as long as it is written & audited properly), gas falling below expectations and no hacks disrupting the process. 
LFG! https://t.co/uD5dSGRPpe

PPS: Having been a holder since I minted my Genesis KaijuKingz.. they hold a special place in my heart as my virgin blue-chip experience. So, whatever I write might be biased since Kaiju is my first love <3. https://t.co/Fi5UDqN9P5

PS: I wrote a bit more about @Augminted since they are the team that is leading @KaijuKingz and I feel that having a strong team is more important than anything else. You might buy into a project for the art but if you want to hold a long-term project, buy into the team.

Barring the fact that there might be a couple of episodes of failure, the team that bounces back the fastest and hardest usually shows a mark of quality andâ€¦ letâ€™s leave it at that. https://t.co/1PCZK4vdPW
As it stands, I am bullish on MKK & the @augminted team, having spoken to a few of them before. I believe that whatever the team touches, will most definitely turn into gold.

For what it is worth, Mutant KaijuKingz would definitely grow to be something interesting and I canâ€™t wait for @Augminted to start branching out into the Metaverse where everything comes together and meld into a huge immersive experience for all holders. https://t.co/F2oaxWnwje

From sources, MKK would definitely be a good opportunity to get into the KKâ€™s ecosystem. Minting is also happening with the team being transparent in what will take place & that marks a good project over an average one â€“ with everything being looked through & made known.

The one that I was really surprised about was RR because it was really well done â€“ bar the exploits that had been utilised by some. It was really made with a purpose, to allow ppl an immersive experience since the tease about RR a few weeks ago.

People are still excited in KaijuKingz and with Mutants looming on the horizon, there has been a ramp up in activity from crazy quizzes that spanned a few days, to role playing in the server for the lab being broken in and Rooftop Rampage. https://t.co/d65wXiKZRX

Back to the Mutant KaijuKingz project..
Take a look at the art, the level of details & the intricacy.
MKK is also launching during turbulent times, w/ R & U on the cusp of something devastating â€“ a look at the statistics of the engagement on @KaijuKingz portrays a telling tale.

Also not to mention, @KaijuKingz is in a partnership with @Coinbase_NFT which could potentially bring more eyes to the project and as such bring in a whole boatload of volume to technically launch them on a moon mission trajectory. https://t.co/AjRcxxpRvF

Next, the Game Director as well as the Co-founder of @Augminted, @YungGatzby. Having had accolades such as Ex-FAANG and Berkeley grad on his resume, he is a stellar contender with his boat load of experiences which includes making indie games for the last 5 years. https://t.co/AldBm5dH9V

The creativity and how much it stands out is the very reason why most people are still rocking their @KaijuKingz PFP. It also stands out to people since KaijuKingz is considered a blue-chip project (subjective but I feel that they are), and the demand for it is still very strong.

Then, we have to talk about the art. The art for @KaijuKingz was and is still considered to be one of the best, which is led by @FutureBoy3LLL who is also a Co-founder of @Augminted. https://t.co/74H7JBe2s0
@n0xscape and joining forces with a few others to launch @KaijuKingz. Talk about taking the road less travelled aye?

He started off with a vague idea how things would develop, back in June 2021 & it was a rather refreshing take that he jumped head in towards the unknown world of Web3. Without connections & a game plan, he forged his own path from applying to @Garyveeâ€™s Scholarship to creating https://t.co/xoKbRprfCe

Let's speak about the team now shall we? The Founder - @ohDotss, is noted as head blockchain engineer with a background in Business Consulting and leads the Strategy portion as acting CEO. 
PS: He follows me too... â™¥ï¸ https://t.co/8Io7vSWAVN

@augminted is thus recognised as a team which wants to integrate and synergise #GameFi & Web3 with more than just meaningful experiences. However, donâ€™t be mistaken because even though @KaijuKingz fall under @augminted, they might just branch out and start their own pet projects. https://t.co/ccBE1eo5nc

Much can be said about the team executing it & they assembled a team that led the NFT frontier, where they quizzes, competitions and contests were done to build the brand. Through KK's outreach, they also helped various projects, even aiding in contract vetting & all things Web3.
Ultimately, the project was a hit regardless, with the Genesis collection hitting a floor of 4.4E upon the soft-relaunch. https://t.co/pRJs39h2C7

As it happened, @KaijuKingz didnâ€™t have the smoothest project launch â€“ being marred & disrupted by various issues which led to Failed Experiment & we are finally seeing the use case of it with this new launch.

They aim to build the future of Web3 through augMINTING NFTs, hence the name.. and most notably led one of the biggest projects in 2021 â€“ @KaijuKingz, and are now expanding the project to include Mutants in the line-up. https://t.co/nZRViLc4rQ

Some background info, @KaijuKingz is developed & designed by @augminted Labs & they have been pumping out stuff not only in KK but other projs as well.
They are a group of people who specialises in Smart contract, P2E gaming, Web3 Dev as well as a whole load correlating to Web3.

One of the hottest topics in Q1 2022 (other than the FUDs and the rugs..), Iâ€™m sure everyone has at least heard of them before and they are none other than Mutant @KaijuKingz.
